info:
岗位职责
1、负责公司及品牌创意设计，包括品牌、产品推广画面及物料，(如电商设计，包装，宣传画册，广告海报，展示道具等) 工作；
2、根据公司品牌需求，提供符合要求的视觉设计;
3、配合品牌推广策划及执行工作，把控对应的平面创意制作沟通等工作;
4、完成上级领导交办的其它任务。

任职要求
1、对创意、设计充满热情；
2、美术、设计相关专业出身;
3、熟练运用Photoshop、AI等设计软件；
4、有动态设计经验者优先

Duties and responsibilities:

-Support internal content development including monthly news, newsflash, etc.;
-Draft social media posts and prepare the lay-out design for wechat posts;
-Translate various communications materials, including Chinese into English and English into Chinese;
-Help manage communication channels including intranet, website, weibo, wechat, etc;
-Provide support to internal and external campaigns and events;
-Help with other ad hoc tasks.

Skills and requirements:

-Major in multi-media, communications, ads, English, Journalism and other relevant fields is preferred;
-Relevant experience in translation and social media management;
-Good spoken and written communication ability in both English and Chinese;
-Good visual/digital software applications skills such as PS, Illustrator, Premier, photography is a plus;
-Proactive, organized, self-motivated and attention to detail;
-Available to work at least 3 days per week and able to start ASAP for at least 3 months.

Transportation Part:

1. Check the accuracy of invoice report between the whole Asia plants(9 countries and 25 plants) and 6 world level forwarders via our advanced system by monthly basis;
2. Analyze the shipment data and figure out the optimization for our stars, for instance, dig our space utilization or try to explore an alternative transportation model;

Forwarder(Suppliers) Management Part:
1. Estimate forwarders performance through our internal standard. During this period, you have the opportunity to reform and improve the criteria of forwarder selection & evaluation;
2. Prepare and participate into the quarterly business meeting with forwarders.

Others:
1. Have enormous challenging projects and you are not just focus on transportation, you will act as the back up to support another function like warehouse & packaging, which means you are able to confront the most comprehensive dimension of supply chain.
2. Some activities support, like workshop, dept meeting preparation, etc.;

Job Requirement:

1.	Excellent English skills;
2.	Prefer candidates whose major is in supply chain, industry engineering, logistics, economics, etc.;
3.	Photography and video recording skills is a plus;
4.	More than 3 days/W,  6 months at least ;

绝对不水的实习，所在部门是供应链的核心部门，有无限多的机会rotate 在 transportation and forwarder management, warehouse management, packaging之间，收获超满足的实习体验，喜欢供应链的小伙伴绝对不要错过这个在汽车龙头行业实习的机会;
Nice 的团队氛围与高大上的工作环境; 
顶尖汽车行业的高含金量实习证明;
